::DrillBit::

He still was in the BlackFortrese's command center, when the message
came through the comm.
"Interesting..."
He opened a comm to DarkFate.
"I trust you heard that thing about the traders. I know that the middle
of a battle isn't the best time, but I want to take advantage of this.
I'm going to send Dollen with some energon cubes. What do you think?"
He turned to Dollen.
"You heard, go!"

::Dollen::

He quickly ran and got some energon cubes, and a rocket pack. He then
made his way out of the base, and took off for the traders.
